The Coilhose Pneumatics Blow-Off System features either a single or double 12" flexible stay-put hose that allows for precise positioning of the air stream. When used, the Blow-Off System can evacuate chips and debris or even cool a work piece. Air Blow-Off systems are great for machinists or woodworkers.

  • High Flow Nozzles Based on the Typhoon Blow Gun
  • Flexflow Hoses Enable Precise Positioning of Nozzles
  • Strong Magnetic Base, Secure Placement
  • Equipped with 1/4" Industrial Interchange Connector
  • Adjustable Flow Using the Supplied Needle Valve
  • Made in USA
Product Information
DescriptionVariable Control Flexflow Blowoff, 12 inch, Single Nozzle
UPC ID029292104418

The Durawhip was designed to be installed on a jackhammer as a lightweight whip hose. When a lighter hose is connected to a jackhammer, it reduces the weight felt by the operator. Durawhip hoses also extend the life of rubber hoses air lines by isolating the vibration from a jackhammer, when installed between the tool and the supply line.

  • Reusable Fittings with Strain Reliefs
  • Composed of Durable, Flexeel Reinforced Polyurethane
  • Made in USA
